<div class="news grid_25 alpha omega">

  {{> header}}

  <div class="news-story">
    <div class="news-story__main">
      <h3 class="news-story__title">So, what are the benefits of a waterproof phone?</h3>
      <div class="news-story__body">
        <p>We know you want to take your phone with you wherever you go – so it’s important for Xperia devices to be well protected. But, just in case you weren’t clear on why we put so much effort into making sure your phone is ready for those clumsy moments or last minute rainstorms, check out the infographic we’ve created.</p>
        <p>You can download a high-res, print resolution version of the infographic by clicking the button below...</p>
      </div>
      <a class="sony-button js-lightbox" href="#" data-file-path="images/news/waterproof-phone-benefits-infographic.jpg">View</a>
      <a class="sony-button" href="http://bit.ly/1pL3gP6">Download</a>
    </div>
    <div class="news-story__aside">
      <img class="news-story__image" src="images/news/waterproof-phone-benefits-infographic-preview.png" alt="Preview image of the benefits of a waterproof phone infographic"/>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- scripts -->
<script type="text/javascript">

function initPage() {
  head.load(prefixURL + "js/fancybox/jquery.fancybox-1.3.4.css");
  head.load(prefixURL + "js/fancybox/jquery.fancybox-1.3.4.js", function() {
    // prefix any lightbox URLs
    $('.js-lightbox').each(function () {
      $(this).attr('href', prefixURL + $(this).data('file-path')).fancybox();
    });
  });
}

</script>
